data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! MOTIVATED SELLER! RARE FIND! Located in the quaint community of Vinwood Estates where you'll find Acre+ Horse Properties with Underground Flood Irrigation. Home features split 3 bed/2 bath floorplan with lots of natural light.Spacious great room includes floor to ceiling stacked-stone fireplace & leads into the kitchen with large island, breakfast nook and separate desk/or coffee nook.Porcelain wood look tile in main living areas.Extra Large master bedroom and Extra Large walk-in shower with multiple shower heads,large walk-in closet.Spacious secondary bedrooms.Oversized 3 car garage with built in storage shelves.New perimeter fencing. Open Breezeway Barn, 5 stalls, tack room/or workshop, wash area & auto waterer. 3 separate RV gates around property for easy access
